snippet.title: Puppies Out [By Zatun] iOS Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Puppies Out by Zatun Android, iOS,iPhone,iPad Gameplay HD video of Puppies Out Game.

PUPPIES OUT! THE CUTEST, FUN AND ORIGINAL ENDLESS RUNNING GAME!

Attention all fun and puppy lovers out there!

Puppies Out! is a free 3D Infinite Runner game for kids featuring a lovely cute pet – named “Buddy Lab” – alongside with some of its adorable puppy friends including “Hippie“, “Amigo“, “Rocky“, “Sir Beagle“, “Posh Pup” , “Super Hero“, “Bandit” and “Valentine“.

They live in a happy, fantasy dog world where running is the key to success! Tough obstacles and challenges await them, but the puppies are ready for it!

EXPLORE 3D INFINITE RUNNER’S GREAT FEATURES:

• Explore Fun-Tasy Puppy Worlds!
• Enjoy Gorgeous Graphics while collecting life-saving Silver Bones.
• 21 cute and legendary puppies as playable characters to choose from
• Personalize your pet game and collect amazing Paw-Ur-Ups!
• Run through a colorful, lively 3D landscape
• Increase mission levels and difficulty: run through residential areas, garden areas, bridges, construction areas and parks.
• Upgrades available as you play: Shields, Mystery Boxes, Magnetic Collars, Frisbee and Jet Packs
• Share the fun of a 3D Infinite Runner on Facebook and get Rewarded
• Get rewarded with Lives as you win or via sharing the App on social media


This top exciting dog game for kids and adults just need you to bring them to life.
In this unique and best puppy game every level is an adventure and every mission is a discovery. Make sure you win and never stop running!

Let the puppies out! & start playing! Make the most of the running, racing and chasing! In this lovely kids game Puppy Dog does it all!

http://www.techzamazing.com
http://www.facebook.com/techzamazing
http://twitter.com/techzamazing
